442
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,400
Was Shen Yan the culprit?

443
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:21,520
Xu Shu is terrible.

444
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:23,959
Lock him up with
the prisoners on death row

445
00:23:24,479 --> 00:23:25,800
