Hanchen's reputation.

489
00:24:42,439 --> 00:24:44,359
Shen Zhaowen is the niece
of Noble Consort Cao.

490
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:45,359
In the harem,

491
00:24:45,359 --> 00:24:46,800
